00:37:01,453 --> 00:37:03,553
That's coward talk.

434
00:37:04,289 --> 00:37:07,290
I ain't no coward.

435
00:37:24,309 --> 00:37:25,308
( chopping continues )

436
00:37:25,310 --> 00:37:27,744
- Pa.
- Thank you, Abby.

437
00:37:39,391 --> 00:37:41,291
Sammy.

