783
01:07:06,056 --> 01:07:07,155
a good-for-nothing
coward.

784
01:07:07,157 --> 01:07:08,523
He ain't like him.

785
01:07:14,731 --> 01:07:17,432
Why are you
defending him?

786
01:07:19,736 --> 01:07:22,537
